{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML Element-Referenz","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"math","title":"math","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Dies ist eine alphabetische Liste aller MathML<strong>-Darstellungselemente</strong> (engl. presentation markup). Damit können innerhalb einer html-Umgebung mathematische Terme und Gleichungen dargestellt werden.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p>Hinweis: Damit nicht zu verwechseln ist die inhaltliche Beschreibung eines mathematischen Terms oder einer Gleichung (engl. content markup). Die inhaltliche Beschreibung ist nicht dafür gedacht, unmittelbar vom MathML-Parser innerhalb von html-Seiten dargestellt zu werden.&nbsp; (siehe <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=276028\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;276028</a>). Wenn Du mehr über das content markup lernen möchtest, dann besuche <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter4.html\" rel=\" noopener\">Kapitel 4</a> der <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3-Spezifikation</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"multiColumnList\" id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code> (Wurzelelement, Top-level element)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"a\">A</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\" title=\"<maction>\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></code> (Mit einem Ausdruck verknüpfte Aktion)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maligngroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;maligngroup&gt;</a></code> (Alignment group)<span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/malignmark\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;malignmark&gt;</a></code> (Alignment points)<span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"e\">E</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\" title=\"<menclose>\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></code> (Umrandung/Markierung)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\" title=\"<merror>\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></code> (Fehler im Ausdruck hervorheben)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"f\">F</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"<mfenced>\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></code> (Klammern setzen)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"<mfrac>\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></code> (Bruch)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"g\">G</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code> (Displaying non-standard symbols) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"i\">I</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"<mi>\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></code> (Bezeichner, engl. identifier)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"l\">L</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlabeledtr\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlabeledtr&gt;</a></code> (Labeled row in a table or a matrix) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlongdiv\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlongdiv&gt;</a></code> (Long division notation) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"m\">M</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt; (en-US)</a></code> (Prescripts and tensor indices)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"n\">N</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\" title=\"<mn>\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></code> (Wert, engl. number)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"o\">O</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"<mo>\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></code> (Rechenzeichen, Operator)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\" title=\"<mover>\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></code> (Akzent/Grenzwert oberhalb des Ausdrucks)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"p\">P</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"<mpadded>\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></code> (Innenabstand hinzufügen)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\" title=\"<mphantom>\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></code> (Platz für unsichtbaren Ausdruck)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"r\">R</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\" title=\"<mroot>\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></code> (Wurzel <em>mit</em> ausgeschriebenem Exponenten)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\" title=\"<mrow>\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></code> (Ausdrücke gruppieren)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"s\">S</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"<ms>\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></code> (Zeichenkette)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarries\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarries&gt;</a></code> (Annotations such as carries) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarry\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarry&gt;</a></code> (Single carry, child element of <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarries\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarries&gt;</a></code>) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msgroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msgroup&gt;</a></code> (Grouped rows of <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code> and <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlongdiv\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlongdiv&gt;</a></code> elements) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msline\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msline&gt;</a></code> (Horizontal lines inside <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code> elements) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code> (Leerraum)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\" title=\"<msqrt>\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></code> ([Quadrat-]Wurzel, <em>ohne</em> angegebenen Exponenten)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msrow\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msrow&gt;</a></code> (Rows in <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code> elements) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code> (Stacked alignment) <span class=\"notecard inline warning\">Nicht implementiert</span></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"<mstyle>\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></code> (Änderung der Darstellung)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\" title=\"<msub>\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></code> (Subscript, tiefergestellte Zahl)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"<msup>\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></code> (Superscript, Exponent, höhergestellte Zahl)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"<msubsup>\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></code> (Höher- <em>und</em> tiefergestellte Zahl)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"t\">T</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"<mtable>\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></code> (Tabelle oder Matrix)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"<mtd>\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></code> (Zelle in einer Tabelle oder Matrix)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"<mtext>\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></code> (Text)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"<mtr>\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></code> (Zeile in einer Tabelle oder Matrix)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"u\">U</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\" title=\"<munder>\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></code> (Akzent/Grenzwert unterhalb des Ausdrucks)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"<munderover>\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></code> (Akzente/Grenzwerte ober- und unterhalb des Ausdrucks)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"other_elements\">Other elements</h3>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;semantics&gt; (en-US)</a></code> (Container for semantic annotations)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/annotation\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;annotation&gt;</a></code> (Data annotations)</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/annotation-xml\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;annotation-xml&gt;</a></code> (XML annotations)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML\">MathML</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute\">MathML Attribut-Referenz</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Dies ist eine alphabetische Liste aller MathML-Darstellungselemente (engl. presentation markup). Damit können innerhalb einer html-Umgebung mathematische Terme und Gleichungen dargestellt werden.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MathML element reference","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Referencia de elementos de MathML","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Référence des éléments MathML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MathML 要素リファレンス","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MathML element reference","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Справка по элементам MathML","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"MathML 元素参考","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/mathml/element","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/mathml/element/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML Element-Referenz"}],"pageTitle":"MathML Element-Referenz - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}